data.description:
10,000.00 in concessions for the buyer. Premarket Appraisal completed on the home dated October 2023. List price is based off of the premarket appraisal. Buyer can have copy once they are under contract.
Welcome home! 3 bedroom, 2 full baths on a corner lot. Boasts recently renovated kitchen updated fixtures ,updated cabinets, gorgeous Quartz counter tops , custom tile back splash, stainless steel appliances, updated light fixture. Newer flooring throughout with laminate, carpet and tile flooring in the bathrooms. Guest bathroom has a beautiful new vanity. Newer commodes and sink fixtures. Will repair deck rails and other small repairs. Your buyer will absolutely love this one!  A Sweet and Cozy gem just in time for the Holidays.
